Before you hit ‘Enter your pincode & click on 'Buy with Exchange' to check if the Exchange Offer is available in your location. Exchange is possible in eligible pincodes Once you’ve decided which phone to buy, provide details of your old phone in the Exchange Offer form to get discount. Keep you IMEI No. handy.Once the order is placed, the new phone will be shipped. Hand in your old phone, in working condition, to the field executive at the time of delivery.
